From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Your Name [you@example.com](mailto:you@example.com)
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove pybind11 per-interpreter GIL declarations

The Emscripten toolchain currently does not require nor fully support
the pybind11 per-interpreter GIL and free-threading declarations used
by these extension modules.

Remove the declarations and use the standard PYBIND11_MODULE form.

---

scikitplot/nc/_linalg/src/module_linalg.cpp      | 2 --
scikitplot/nc/_version/src/module_version.cpp    | 2 --
tools/submodules/vendored_NumCpp/src/nc.cpp      | 2 --
3 files changed, 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/scikitplot/nc/_linalg/src/module_linalg.cpp b/scikitplot/nc/_linalg/src/module_linalg.cpp
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/scikitplot/nc/_linalg/src/module_linalg.cpp
+++ b/scikitplot/nc/_linalg/src/module_linalg.cpp
@@ -21,8 +21,6 @@ PYBIND11_MODULE(
_linalg,
m,

* py::mod_gil_not_used(),
* py::multiple_interpreters::per_interpreter_gil()
  ){
  // -------- Module Docstring --------

diff --git a/scikitplot/nc/_version/src/module_version.cpp b/scikitplot/nc/_version/src/module_version.cpp
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/scikitplot/nc/_version/src/module_version.cpp
+++ b/scikitplot/nc/_version/src/module_version.cpp
@@ -21,8 +21,6 @@ PYBIND11_MODULE(
__version,
m,

* py::mod_gil_not_used(),
* py::multiple_interpreters::per_interpreter_gil()
  ){
  // -------- Module Docstring --------

diff --git a/tools/submodules/vendored_NumCpp/src/nc.cpp b/tools/submodules/vendored_NumCpp/src/nc.cpp
index 0000000..0000000 100644
--- a/tools/submodules/vendored_NumCpp/src/nc.cpp
+++ b/tools/submodules/vendored_NumCpp/src/nc.cpp
@@ -21,8 +21,6 @@ PYBIND11_MODULE(
nc,
m,

* py::mod_gil_not_used(),
* py::multiple_interpreters::per_interpreter_gil()
  ){
  // -------- Module Docstring --------
  --
  2.49.0
